globally as well, but also

00:53:25.600 --> 00:53:26.585 align:middle line:90%
water rights.

00:53:26.585 --> 00:53:30.775 align:middle line:84%
This is becoming-- this will
become the next major fight

00:53:30.775 --> 00:53:31.575 align:middle line:90%
on the planet.

00:53:31.575 --> 00:53:32.491 align:middle line:90%
>>SHEEHAN: Absolutely.

00:53:32.491 --> 00:53:34.900 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And we need to see
what our rights are, what

